<span>[5]</span>
</a>=C2=A0For another thing, traditionally if you are going to sell the deb=
t you send investors an offering memorandum describing the company, its bus=
iness plan, its financials, etc., and how do you do that here? The <a href=
=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/29560330.279505/aHR0cHM6L=
y93d3cuZnQuY29tL2NvbnRlbnQvZDE4NzlkMGMtYzUyZS00ZjQ4LTgyZjAtMDk0NThhZGQ0YWVl=
